                "text": "<p><strong>Pour It Forward: Endometriosis Foundation of America</strong></p><p>March is Endometriosis Awareness Month, and we’re donating 10% of our proceeds to the Endometriosis Foundation of America.</p><p>Endometriosis affects 1 in 10 women, yet many are still told their pain is “just a bad period.” It isn’t.<br/>This foundation supports research, education, and advocacy so more women get real answers and better care.</p><p>By shopping with us, you’re helping push for better answers, earlier diagnoses, and better care for women with endometriosis.</p><p>Thank you for helping us pour into something bigger. 💛</p>",
